      "date": "2012-10-07 00:28:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e9ddcdc8-1012-11e2-85d6-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
